{
  "texts": [
    "Toward showing x 1 ⊑ s x 3, supposez 1 ⊑ x 1.",
    "Then given x 1 ⊑ s x 2, there is some z ′ 1 ⊑ z 1 such that z ′ 1 ⊑ x 2.",
    "Then given x 2 ⊑ s x 3, there is some z ′ 2 ⊑ z ′ 1 such that z ′ 2 ⊑ x 3.",
    "Given z ′ 2 ⊑ z ′ 1 ⊑ z 1, by the transitivity of ⊑ we have z ′ 2 ⊑ z 1.",
    "Thus, for any z 1 ⊑ x 1 there is a z ′ 2 ⊑ z 1 such that z ′ 2 ⊑ x 3, which implies x 1 ⊑ s x 3."
  ]
}